sentences: Takuya Asanuma (浅沼 拓也, Asanuma Takuya, born 9 September 1971), better known mononymously as Takuya (stylized in all caps as TAKUYA), is a Japanese musician, singer, songwriter and record producer.
He currently works as a solo artist under the name Takuya and also had a solo project called Robots which was dissolved in 2009.
